  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we found out there was a carriage of food in that train.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we-- there was an air raid on, so we broke open that carriage.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we started robbing all-- the German SS were laying under the, under the-- the train because they were frightened of the-- the bombs.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We didn't care if we were bombed or not.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We just ripped open the carriage, and we got hold of whatever we-- I got hold of a basket of raw eggs.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I vaulted over to our wagon.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And within two minutes, there's nothing left of the raw eggs.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We all finished them off, the broke and unbroken egg.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, this train stopped specially under that bridge because the Germans didn't want this bridge should be bombed.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they knew that if the pilots would see us under the bridge, they won't bomb the bridge.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they didn't bomb that bridge.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's how they got saved as well, the SS.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Anyway, after about a day we were moved on further and further.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then finally we arrived outside Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
